Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:42.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, no one has \Never fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:51.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:57.39,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the \NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled \Nby the Four Emperors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.66,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and landed on Punk Hazard;\Nan island with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,two parts, one burning, \Nthe other frozen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.41,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They learned about the puppet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.63,Italics,,0,0,0,,master of Shinokuni - \NCaesar Clown's motive{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and along with their pirate \Nally - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,\Nwere drawn into a climactic battle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}which ended with Caesar's defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten anything until today,f\Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must've been hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry \Nabout anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope that everybody \Nelse is okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,let's keep living, Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...you gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, they started the victory banquet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It's Time to Say Goodbye!\NLeaving Punk Hazard!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't really think that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI'll keep my promise with a pirate like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you really wanted to silence me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there were several occasions \Nthat you could've killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to,\Ntaking advantage of Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking advantage of him?\NMaybe he's taking advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of the Four Emperors \Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kaido, the King of the Beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Shanks is not \Nthe first one to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI have no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...I plan to beat all \Nof the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beat all of the Four Emperors"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We share a mutual interest\Nbut you're underestimating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the emperors of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who have skirmished over territories \Neven against Whitebeard himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, they say Kaido, \Nthe King of the Beasts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nis the strongest creature in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? He's not even a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ally with each other \Nuntil we kill Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And our chances of success are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just say they're really low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! We shouldn't go \Nalong with this, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no particular reason
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't kill you, White Chase-{\i1}ya{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about going to Green Bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can handle the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He can barely lift the kid up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...Big-eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Luffy, you're big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stretchy!\N--Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are kind of nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We are the fearsome Navy G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all ready now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys were \Ngonna take the tanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, because Nami \Nand Chopper claimed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not going anywhere until \Nwe see the children sailing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pain to wait \Nfor other Navy people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so take the tanker with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on board, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take you home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to hurry. One by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If the tanker is ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think of crossing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,\NThis is the line between good and evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't step on it! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?! You were enjoying the banquet\Na few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! No, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,About that, we really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys are pirates!\NA dishonor to the human race!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--Where is the robot?\N--Oh? Where are the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that down! How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,\NEven just looking at pirates hurts your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are not so \Ndifferent from us, G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But they got on board safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Brother!\N--Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the champions of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're gonna exterminate all pirates\Nwho cause civilians grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are the scum of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're men of justice!\NDon't let the kids see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--Sis!\N--Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You shouldn't see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,--Brother!\N--Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--They lifted it up!\N--Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't see them, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see them well \Nand yelling like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'll ask Vegapunk for \Nassistance about their treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Mini-Merry\Nafter we took it to get to the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Robin! You're the fifth person\Nto ask that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make eye-contact \Nwith those trashy pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,\NIt'll ruin your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But we Navy won't let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're men of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadly gas from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Run if you don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... men of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiral-eyebrowed brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna say goodbye to \Npirates, you're a bad kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say "Thank you" to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll drag you out of the \Ntanker and leave you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Pirates are bad \Nand the Navy is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates have been causing \Nso much chaos in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that even \Nif you're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never forgive pirates!\NBecause we should not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! Unforgivable!\NPirates are unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!\NSay "No" to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!\NPirates are unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!\NSay "No" to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we asked them to help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they helped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even know \Nwhat was going on with us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but they took us with them\Nwithout being bothered by our size!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go home soon! Hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing on the island\Nand no one had come to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But they came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That we didn't find you sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates stink and they're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Navy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...always clean and beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are a bunch of cowards\Nand they're sloppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!\NThe Navy is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't let us say \N"Thank you" to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want pirates!\NThe Navy is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in contrast, the Navy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...very brave and righteous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tashigi-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nunless we keep saying bad things about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we will start...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,liking these outlaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even though they're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're odd Navy soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate brothers and sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When we grow up, we will become...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get good rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get home,\Nyou deserve to be spoiled by
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,your father and mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids! You gotta eat something healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is good considering \Nit's the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know the sea will be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is he coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! We haven't told \Nyou about the alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy got us involved in trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Next time we see you,\Nwe'll take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're our enemy next time!\N--Be ready for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We will catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, what's your name?!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somebody please help me! I'm on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Punk Hazard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,NHC10.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I detected it in their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it was just a trace amount,\Nit's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...a drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are children who were
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,kidnapped two years ago \Nin this laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal a ship and let's \Nescape from Punk Hazard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you up and kidnap you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can! But I'm protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo! The Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even have balls to \Npick a fight with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...picking fights all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Grizzly Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like those squirts \Nhave the devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the \NSky Path ended there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! That bastard Law \Nreally betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!\NI want to pay for it with death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You needed me but I couldn't please you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a life yacht \Nthat was on our tanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!\NAfter I hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You don't have to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You two were just following my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a surprise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect the boss \Nhimself to show up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,\NIt's a shame that you're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're looking for \NCaesar, he's with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J-Joker! Help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Baby 5 and Buffalo's bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me about \Nsuch frivolous things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's negotiate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Law, come to your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A squirt like you shouldn't \Nimitate what grown-ups do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?\NDon't make me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make you mad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your most important business partner is\None of the Four Emperors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The big-time pirate - Kaido, \Nthe King of the Beasts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I know you can't make \Nhim mad at any cost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would happen if he finds out\Nyou can't produce SMILE anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since he's not the negotiating type,\Nthere'll probably be a fierce battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, you're turning blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he'll destroy you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you carried the joke too far, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want in exchange for Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,\NName your price.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Resign from the Seven Warlords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this squirt-{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he can no longer stay in Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I want is for you \Nto abandon everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,\Nthat you spent a decade to attain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and go back to being \Na common pirate again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:12.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,the Admirals from the Navy HQ\Nwill hunt you down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm expecting to see it in the newspaper\Ntomorrow morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your resignation from the Warlords is\Nin the paper,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will call you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't see it, the \Nnegotiation is off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn squirt!
